---
title: Quick Creamy Beef & Pork Veggie Pasta with Parmesan
description: This saucy creation uses a creamy tomato sauce to coat fusilli, with chunks of tender mince and flavoursome Parmesan. Add greens that gently wilt when tossed with the pasta, and you’ve got a new recipe that's sure to please everyone.

